text: Sándor Török (14 February 1881 - 13 February 1939) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed at the 1906 Intercalated Games and the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1881 births Category:1939 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1906 Intercalated Games Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
